Entries.default: "Ikawha blunts her teeth speaking to this Clario. He does not care for us."
"If you would speak, speak to Ikawha. She is with the Vailians."
"Greetings, brother. Our chieftain is away, speaking to the outsiders."
Entries.female: "Greetings, brother. Our chieftain is away, speaking to the outsiders."

Entries.default: "Keep the peace, and all will be well."
"You! You will pay in blood for what you have done!"
